Package: rrlmgraphbench
Type: Package
Title: Benchmark Suite for rrlmgraph
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("David", "Schoch", email = "davidrsch@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides fixture projects and ground-truth datasets for
    benchmarking the rrlmgraph package.  Fixtures range from a minimal
    data-science script project to a medium-sized Shiny application and a
    small R package, covering the full spectrum of project types supported
    by rrlmgraph.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    cli,
    fs,
    rrlmgraph
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/davidrsch/rrlmgraph-bench
BugReports: https://github.com/davidrsch/rrlmgraph-bench/issues
